ARGUMENT

| Step | Hyp | Ref | Expression |

| 1 |  | #P_ax-in1 | |- ( ( ph -> -. ph ) -> -. ph ) |
\
 Reductio ad absurdum.  Theorem *2.01 of [WhiteheadRussell] p. 100.  This is valid intuitionistically (in the terminology of Section 1.2 of [Bauer] p. 482 it is a proof of negation not a proof by contradiction); compare with ~ pm2.18dc which only holds for some propositions.  (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 12-May-2015.)
